This plate has #inippu😋 #kasappu😖 #thuvarpu😒 & my #makkal will eat this without showing #salippu🙄 #veruppu😫 #kaduppu😡 because eating junk "often" is #thappu🙆 & will give you #aapu😩 . Also Remember, taking care of your health is your own #poruppu 🙋.
.
On my plate with #karuppu color items (just sharing whatever is practised at home.),
💮 Angaya podi with Ghee. This has manthakali /black nightshade berry, sundaikkai/turkey berry, neem flower, Kandathipli, arisi thipli (pepper varieties), dry ginger & many more. Good for digestion.
💮 Vepampoo mor rasam / Neem flower buttermilk rasam - This is consumed hot after recovering from cold.
💮Sweet potato fry - this is the combo to balance the bitterness specially given at our home to make kids like these recipes.
